<h1>Thank you for joining our coronavirus research volunteer list</h1>

<p> We appreciate your commitment to helping others through this important research effort.</p>

<h2>If we think you may be eligible for one of our research studies</h2>

<p>We'll contact you to tell you more about it so you can decide if you want to join</p>
<p>Please understand that some studies have specific requirements. So it may be weeks or months before there's a study that you may be eligible to join.</p>
<p><em>Note</em>: We'll never ask for an ID number or for your financial, credit, or bank account information over the phone. For tips on how to aviod coronavirus-related scams, visit the <a href="https://www.ftc.gov/coronavirus/scams-consumer-advice">Federal Trade Comission website</a></p>

<h2>If we don't think you may be eligible for any studies</h2>

<p>We won't contact you. But we'll keep your information on file for future studies you may be eligible to join.</p>
